      "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.class-features\" data-id=\"sobLlAGQkmWcFBFx\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Magic Hack</a></p>\n        <p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl18_LabelName\">As a standard action, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to temporarily learn how to use a weapon in combat. Choose a single weapon; you gain proficiency with it (and any identical weapon) for a number of minutes equal to your class level. Each round you use the weapon reduces this magic hackâ€™s duration by 1 minute. For example, at 4th level, you could gain proficiency with corona laser rifles for 4 minutes. If you fire such a weapon for 2 rounds, you remain proficient with it for 2 more minutes.</span></p>",
